snippet.title: VR Boxing -TrueBoxingVR Gameplay
snippet.description:
This clip shows a 3x1min gameplay of TrueBoxingVR. there is a side by side video showing what is visible in the VR headset for the player, and the other recording of the player.
Download Demo on Steam or App Lab
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2556620/True_Boxing_VR/
Quest AppLab: https://www.meta.com/s/a8rWIvdKX
